{
  "stem": "4361.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they put us like about 10 or 15, as many as we were in those bunks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they gave one dish, and they put that slop, which was allegedly some sort of a soup, and each one was supposed to take so many sips from that one bowl.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just passed it to the next girl, because who was going to do that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they left it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first day, the second day, the third day, it was different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The third day, we began eating the slop, because we were beginning to starve, because there was nothing else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They kept us for about four weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, here, I don't have the exact time element, because you forget dates.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You forget-- it's not that you forget.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You don't know anymore whether it's the 15th or the 18th.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just know it's day, and it's night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's another day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's another night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after about four weeks, I believe, we were quarantined, which meant we were kept in that particular block.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we learned what [NON-ENGLISH] appell, meaning roll call, was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they kept counting us three times a day-- early in the morning, midday, and in the evening or at sundown.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When I say early in the morning, I mean at dawn when the rouse got us out from the barracks, and then noon, and-- and-- and sundown time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was very little food, and they began-- the rows, we were always in rows of five-- the rows began to thin, because after the person in charge of that particular block where I was, and she was called the blokova-- Polish words-- she set us up.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She organized us in rows of five.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
